      <title>Optum Rx 分销合同结束后康德乐股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/cardinal-health-falls-as-optum-rx-distribution-contract-ended</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在药品分销商康德乐 (Cardinal Health Inc.) 失去与联合健康集团 (UnitedHealth Group Inc.) 药品福利子公司的合同后，该公司股价在早盘交易中大幅下跌。]]></description>
